Installation:
	make

Usage:
  xspy {list | spy [window_id]| help}

  Valid modes :
        list : displays all windows of the display.
        spy : listen the windows for key events.
        help : this help message.

  Parameters :
        window_id : the id of the window to listen.
                    If not specified, listen to all windows

How to change the display?
  $ DISPLAY=host:display program
  Example :
  $ DISPLAY=tx10:0 xspy



